{
  "text": "A Cochrane review of 79 articles (a total of 1999 cases) consisting of open-label case series with three or more cases of primary angioplasty was published in 2006 [CITATION_1] . The safety profile of the procedure showed an overall perioperative rate of stroke of 7.9%, perioperative death of 3.4%, and perioperative stroke or death of 9.5%. Of these studies with a 1-year follow-up the stroke rate at 1 year was 6%.",
